{"title":"西海固风（组诗）","authors":["刘汉立"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":5,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西海固风（组诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘汉立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生于斯，长于斯，我无法摆脱一种乡土情结和家园精神。我只想通过诗的形式勾勒西海固人的困苦辛酸，抗争欢乐，来诠释某种生活的意义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道，只有拥有了精神的支撑点，我才能上路，前行！——题记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龟裂的皮肤和土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要一种滋补"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在征服之外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西海固人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然把老天爷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看得很重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面向黄土背朝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是风景的轮廓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太多的细节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一言难尽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水和着泥土纵横"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的画面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅仅很动人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也很沉重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧羊人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不同于城里的生意人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放牧是乡人的财富"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧羊人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大半生都寄放在大山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶羊上山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便同羊儿一起咀嚼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山和生活的含义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幽幽游遍山峦的眼神里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许透悟了一种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别人永远也不能分享"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的意境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧鞭的脆响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是黄昏的彩虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熨帖在故乡的大山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"及乡村的心房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟丝丝缕缕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家园是生活的起点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亦是生活的终点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚发芽的憧憬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失去在大山的沉默里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩着牛羊的蹄印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你同父辈一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕耘贫瘠收割贫瘠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古石磨前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干瘪的麦粒手中滑落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个巨大的问号从天而降"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗糙的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道需要的仅仅是汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水已流得太多太多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清纯而又焦灼的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿越迢迢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着清脆诱人的铃声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追寻那面冉冉升起的旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声真切的呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动荡了整个华夏大地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借我一双翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将撑出一方灿烂的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄灿烂的麦浪中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥舞镰刀的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突出于整个夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散发成熟气息的小麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷倒地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从父亲的脚下蔓延成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另外一种海洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲挥汗如雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲站起来抹汗的姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论国画油画雕刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是一幅杰作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光依然在额头忙碌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"某种香甜被太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炙烤得更加诱人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随风浸润家园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"及家园以外的亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西海固人笑容舒展喝上了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民子弟兵打出来的甜水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西海固人穿着西装套裙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翩翩起舞一展歌喉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西海固人坐上了火车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上北京下江南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西海固人乘飞机漂洋过海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引进外资兴建家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土豆也变成了金豆豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天…………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西海固人内心感激"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革开放和扶贫开发政策"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西海固人坚信明天会更好"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}